    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-1a' );" name="007-1a" class="pb">[007-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:190'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='190:200'>　三家詩拾遺卷七</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='200:222'>　　　　　　　　　　　柳州府知府范家相撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='222:227'>　小雅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='227:231'>鹿鳴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='231:254'>　魯詩司馬遷曰仁義凌遲鹿鳴刺焉　蔡邕曰鹿鳴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='254:277'>　者周大臣之所作也王道衰大臣知賢者幽隠故彈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='277:294'>　絃諷諫<span class='krp-note'>文選注載/蔡邕琴操</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='294:320'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-1b' );" name="007-1b" class="pb">[007-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='320:343'>　　按左傳明云鹿鳴所以燕嘉賔也魯詩之失與關</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='343:366'>　　雎同吕元鈞氏謂彈絃諷諫及陳古以諷非謂二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='366:381'>　　詩作於衰周其詳巳見關雎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='381:391'>呦呦鹿鳴食野之苹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='391:416'>　　淮南子曰鹿鳴興於獸而君子美之取其得食之相呼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='416:439'>　　美鹿鳴之得食以招羣興君子備笙簧以宴客似</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='439:448'>　　與魯詩不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='448:464'>德音孔昭視民不佻君子是則是傚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='464:490'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-2a' );" name="007-2a" class="pb">[007-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='490:513'>　韓詩鄭氏曰鹿鳴采其已有㫖酒以燕嘉賔嘉賔既</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='513:540'>　來示我以善道又樂其有孔昭之明德可則傚也<span class='krp-note'>鄉/飲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='540:549'>　<span class='krp-note'>酒禮/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='549:572'>　　鄭志答張逸曰注禮時未為詩箋故同舊説此蓋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='572:589'>　　得之張恭伯者然其意正與毛同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='589:593'>四牡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='593:615'>四牡騑騑周道倭遲<span class='krp-note'>韓作威夷漢/書作郁夷</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='615:642'>　韓詩薛君曰威夷險也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span>　班固曰周道郁夷言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='642:668'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-2b' );" name="007-2b" class="pb">[007-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='668:685'>　使臣行馬馳於此道<span class='krp-note'>地理/志</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='685:708'>　　郁夷地名詳王應麟詩地考此魯齊之説與韓異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='708:714'>皇皇者華</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='714:732'>皇皇者華于彼原隰駪駪征夫每懷靡及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='732:755'>　魯詩莘莘征夫每懷靡及夙夜征行猶恐無及况欲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='755:772'>　懷安將安及矣<span class='krp-note'>劉向列/女傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='772:795'>　　國語以毎懷靡及為慮其知有不及故必周爰而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='795:814'>　　諮謀也魯詩慮其征行之不及義淺矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='814:840'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-3a' );" name="007-3a" class="pb">[007-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='840:857'>常棣<span class='krp-note'>韓作夫栘鄂/作蕚同鄭箋</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='857:882'>　韓序夫栘燕兄弟也閔管蔡之失道也<span class='krp-note'>晁氏/詩説</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='882:905'>　　常棣作於周公事詳左氏毛韓之説皆同　爾雅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='905:928'>　　曰唐棣栘又曰常棣棣是一木也有赤白二種實</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='928:951'>　　如櫻桃者赤栘實如郁李而稍白者白栘故一曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='951:978'>　　棣一曰栘若棠<span class='krp-note'>唐/同</span>棣則另是一木亦有赤白二種</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='978:1001'>　　其實如梨而較小其葉無風常自動故曰唐棣之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1001:1024'>　　華偏其反而歐陽永叔胡致堂誤認唐棣為棠棣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1024:1050'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-3b' );" name="007-3b" class="pb">[007-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1050:1073'>　　因以唐棣四句即此篇之逸詩夫子刪詩篇刪其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1073:1083'>　　章蓋未之考也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1083:1108'>和樂且湛<span class='krp-note'>韓作/眈</span>　韓傳眈樂之甚也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1108:1112'>伐木</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1112:1140'>　韓詩伐木廢則友朋之道缺<span class='krp-note'>晁氏/詩説</span>　序曰勞者思其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1140:1163'>　事詩人以伐木苦其事故以為文<span class='krp-note'>太平/御覽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1163:1186'>　　言伐木之事勞苦其聲若求助於衆力者故詩人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1186:1209'>　　取以為求友者興也　按後漢書注云周德始衰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1209:1235'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-4a' );" name="007-4a" class="pb">[007-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1235:1258'>　　頌聲既寝伐木有鳥鳴之刺未知所出大抵亦魯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1258:1265'>　　齊之説</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1265:1269'>天保</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1269:1291'>　齊詩翼奉曰詩有五際君臣父子夫婦朋友兄弟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1291:1314'>　　此為齊詩本義其意蓋以五達道為五際而天保</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1314:1337'>　　一詩為君臣之際耳而纎緯家遂生異説焉漢朗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1337:1360'>　　覬傳曰四始之缺五際之戹此即翼奉説也而孟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1360:1383'>　　康曰五際卯酉午戌亥也隂陽終始際㑹之歲於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1383:1409'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-4b' );" name="007-4b" class="pb">[007-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1409:1432'>　　此則有改變之政也詩汎歴樞云午亥之際為革</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1432:1455'>　　命邜酉之際為改正辰在天門出入候聼夘天保</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1455:1478'>　　也午采芑也亥大明也然則亥為革命一際也亥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1478:1501'>　　又為天門出入候聼二際也卯為隂陽交際三際</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1501:1524'>　　也午為陽謝隂興四際也酉為隂盛陽㣲五際也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1524:1547'>　　其六情則喜怒哀樂好惡是也又曰大明在亥水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1547:1570'>　　始也四牡在寅木始也嘉魚在已火始也鴻雁在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1570:1593'>　　申金始也凡此緯書之説皆本齊詩而推波助瀾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1593:1619'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-5a' );" name="007-5a" class="pb">[007-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1619:1642'>　　初無當於經義者夫匡鼎解頥未嘗託言符命即</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1642:1665'>　　翼奉推時何嘗鑿証詩篇豈轅固生而肯出此亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1665:1675'>　　姑存弗論可耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1675:1685'>天保定爾亦孔之固</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1685:1708'>　韓詩外傳曰天保定爾亦孔之固言天之所以仁義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1708:1720'>　禮智保定人之甚固也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1720:1743'>　　以仁義禮智為保定君身之本義極正大前儒未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1743:1750'>　　曾見及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1750:1776'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-5b' );" name="007-5b" class="pb">[007-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1776:1782'>禴祠烝嘗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1782:1805'>　韓詩内傳禘取毁廟之主皆升合食於太祖祫則羣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1805:1827'>　廟之主悉升於太祖廟<span class='krp-note'>杜氏通典/引内傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1827:1850'>　　按祫禘本是一祭而公羊以春秋經之大事為大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1850:1873'>　　祫後人不明其説遂分為二韓氏亦然詳其文似</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1873:1902'>　　為祫大禘小者知沿誤已在漢初矣<span class='krp-note'>其詳見詩/瀋長發篇</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1902:1909'>無不爾或承</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1909:1926'>　韓詩薛君曰承受也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1926:1952'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-6a' );" name="007-6a" class="pb">[007-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1952:1956'>采薇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1956:1979'>　班固曰穆王之孫懿王時王室遂衰戎狄交侵暴虐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1979:2002'>　中國中國被其苦詩人始作詩疾而歌之曰靡室靡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2002:2018'>　家獫狁之故豈不日戒獫狁孔棘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2018:2041'>　　此詩諸家悉同毛序惟班固作懿王時刺詩亦本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2041:2064'>　　之三家可知夫靡室靡家之語出自遣戍之口則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2064:2087'>　　殷勤撫恤何殊挾纊若為亂離疾苦之作則憂時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2087:2110'>　　告瘁何異四月惟夏何草不黄諸什乎是不待辨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2110:2136'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-6b' );" name="007-6b" class="pb">[007-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2136:2143'>　　而明者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2143:2153'>昔我往矣楊柳依依</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2153:2170'>　韓詩昔始也依依盛貌<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2170:2174'>出車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2174:2197'>　魯詩司馬遷曰戎狄破逐周襄王而立子帶為天子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2197:2220'>　侵盜暴虐中國中國疾之故詩人歌之曰薄伐獫狁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2220:2245'>　至於太原<span class='krp-note'>六/月</span>出車彭彭城彼朔方<span class='krp-note'>出/車</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2245:2268'>　班固曰宣王興師命將征伐詩人美其功曰薄伐獫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2268:2294'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-7a' );" name="007-7a" class="pb">[007-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2294:2310'>　狁至于太原出輿彭彭城彼朔方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2310:2333'>　　按史漢之説諸家皆疑其何以互異如此不知史</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2333:2356'>　　記明云襄王為戎狄所逐中國疾之詩人歌薄伐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2356:2379'>　　之詩傷今而思古未嘗指為襄王之詩也至漢書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2379:2403'>　　乃直以為宣王之詩與毛不同蓋三家之說耳觀下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2403:2426'>　　六月一篇劉歆之說與班氏正同歆非家世申公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2426:2434'>　　之學者乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2434:2438'>枤杜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2438:2464'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-7b' );" name="007-7b" class="pb">[007-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2464:2498'>檀車幝幝<span class='krp-note'>韓作<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2389' title='KR2389' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2389.png'/><img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2389' title='KR2389' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2389.png'/>/車敝也</span>征夫不逺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2498:2527'>　韓傳男子二十行役三十受兵六十還兵<span class='krp-note'>禮記正義/引内傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2527:2531'>魚麗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2531:2541'>物其有矣維其時矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2541:2567'>　魯詩劉向曰物之所以有而不絶者以其時也<span class='krp-note'>說/苑</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2567:2590'>　　此篇下三章即承上三章而詠嘆之下一句所以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2590:2613'>　　申明上句也古說甚長集傳謂多而能嘉㫖而能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2613:2636'>　　齊有而能時是曲全也與古不同　上二章言物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2636:2662'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-8a' );" name="007-8a" class="pb">[007-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2662:2685'>　　之所以多而可貴者惟其嘉也所以旨而不厭者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2685:2708'>　　惟其偕也嘉也偕也時也皆就君子言之荀子曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2708:2727'>　　不敬交不歡欣不時宜物雖㫖弗貴也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2727:2735'>南陔白華華黍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2735:2758'>　孔頴達曰漢世不行毛詩三家不見詩序謂其惟有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2758:2778'>　三百五篇　按此三詩三家所以無說之故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2778:2782'>蓼蕭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2782:2799'>和鸞雝雝<span class='krp-note'>魯作/噰噰</span>萬福攸同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2799:2825'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-8b' );" name="007-8b" class="pb">[007-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2825:2853'>　魯詩和設軾者也鸞設衡也<span class='krp-note'>後漢輿/服志</span>　賈誼曰和鸞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2853:2879'>　噰噰萬福攸同言動以紀度則萬福之所聚也<span class='krp-note'>新/書</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2879:2902'>　韓詩鸞在衡和在軾升車則馬動馬動則鸞鳴鸞鳴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2902:2919'>　則和應<span class='krp-note'>鄭經解注/引韓内傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2919:2942'>　　和與鸞皆鈴也毛傳在軾曰和在鑣曰鸞此據輶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2942:2965'>　　車鸞鑣謂鸞鈴置於馬口之兩傍也鄭氏曰置鸞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2965:2988'>　　於鑣所以異於乘車是乘車之鸞當在軾矣此詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2988:2999'>　　言乘車當依魯韓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2999:3025'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-9a' );" name="007-9a" class="pb">[007-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3025:3029'>湛露</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3029:3047'>厭厭夜飲<span class='krp-note'>韓詩作/愔愔</span>不醉無歸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3047:3074'>　韓傳愔愔和悅之貌<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span>又曰夫飲之禮不脫屨而即</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3074:3097'>　席者謂之禮跣而上堂者謂之宴能飲者飲之不能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3097:3120'>　飲者已謂之醧齊顔色均衆寡謂之沈閉門而不出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3120:3143'>　者謂之湎故君子可以宴可以醧不可以沈不可以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3143:3155'>　湎<span class='krp-note'>初學記/内傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3155:3178'>　　左傳昔諸侯朝正於王王宴樂之於是乎賦湛露</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3178:3204'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-9b' );" name="007-9b" class="pb">[007-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3204:3227'>　　則夭子當陽諸侯用命也毛公據以釋此詩當矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3227:3249'>　　韓以愔愔為和悅而詳引古禮足以備所未備</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3249:3272'>　　文選注載薛君章句曰飲酒之禮下跣而上堂者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3272:3295'>　　謂之宴齊顔色均衆寡謂之流閉門不出謂之湎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3295:3307'>　　與初學記所引小異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3307:3325'>其實離離　韓詩離離長貌<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3325:3329'>菁莪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3329:3355'>菁菁者莪<span class='krp-note'>韓作/蓁蓁</span>　韓詩蓁蓁盛貌<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3355:3382'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-10a' );" name="007-10a" class="pb">[007-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3382:3386'>六月</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3386:3409'>　魯詩劉歆曰周室既衰四夷並侵獫狁最強至宣王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3409:3430'>　而伐之詩人美而頌之<span class='krp-note'>本傳引/六月詩</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3430:3440'>元戎十乘以先啓行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3440:3463'>　韓詩薛君曰元戎大戎車也車有大戎十乘謂車縵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3463:3486'>　輪馬被甲衡軛之上盡有劍㦸名曰陷陣之車所以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3486:3510'>　冒突先啟敵家之行伍也<span class='krp-note'>史記索𨼆/引章句</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3510:3524'>吉甫燕喜既多受祉來歸自鎬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3524:3551'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-10b' );" name="007-10b" class="pb">[007-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3551:3574'>　魯詩劉向曰吉甫之歸周厚賜之其詩曰來歸自鎬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3574:3590'>　千里之鎬猶以為逺<span class='krp-note'>奏/疏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3590:3594'>采芑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3594:3600'>有瑲葱珩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3600:3623'>　韓傳佩玉上有葱珩下有雙璜衝牙蠙珠以納其間</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3623:3636'>　<span class='krp-note'>周禮鄭注/引韓傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3636:3640'>車攻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3640:3652'>東有甫<span class='krp-note'>韓作/圃</span>草</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3652:3679'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-11a' );" name="007-11a" class="pb">[007-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3679:3707'>　韓詩薛君曰圃博也有博大之茂草也<span class='krp-note'>文選注後/漢書注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3707:3730'>　　毛傳甫大也大芟草以為防也與韓不同但鄭箋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3730:3753'>　　又云甫草者甫田之草引鄭有圃田為証以周之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3753:3769'>　　東巡所必經耳則仍用韓說矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3769:3791'>四牡奕奕　韓詩薛君曰奕奕盛也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3791:3795'>吉日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3795:3818'>　齊詩翼奉曰二陽並行王者所以吉午酉也詩曰吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3818:3829'>　日庚午<span class='krp-note'>本/傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3829:3856'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-11b' );" name="007-11b" class="pb">[007-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3856:3879'>　　火盛於午金盛於酉庚即酉也故曰二陽並行一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3879:3902'>　　曰奉時日之學用辰不用日如甲子日用子不用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3902:3925'>　　甲也庚午日取午為陽以王者當之為二陽要非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3925:3931'>　　經義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='3931:3982'>儦儦俟俟<span class='krp-note'>韓作<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1750' title='KR1750' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1750.png'/><img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1750' title='KR1750' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1750.png'/>騃/騃騃音俟</span>　韓詩薛君曰趨曰<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1750' title='KR1750' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1750.png'/>行曰騃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='3982:3991'>　<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='3991:4015'>且以酌醴　韓詩薛君曰醴甜而不泲也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4015:4019'>鴻雁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4019:4046'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-12a' );" name="007-12a" class="pb">[007-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4046:4057'>劬勞于野　百堵皆作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4057:4084'>　韓詩劬數也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span>　又曰八尺為板五板為堵五堵為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4084:4107'>　雉又曰堵四十尺雉二百尺以板長八尺接五板而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4107:4129'>　為堵接五堵而為雉<span class='krp-note'>俱公羊傳/注引内傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4129:4133'>庭燎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4133:4156'>　魯詩劉向曰宣王嘗卧而晏起姜后脱簪珥待罪於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4156:4179'>　永巷使其傅母進言於王曰妾不才妾之淫心見矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4179:4202'>　至使君王失禮而晏起以見君王樂色而淫也敢請</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4202:4229'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-12b' );" name="007-12b" class="pb">[007-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4229:4252'>　婢子之罪宣王感悟於是勤於政事早朝晏卧卒成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4252:4265'>　中興之名<span class='krp-note'>列女/傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4265:4288'>　　毛序美宣王也因以箴之蓋以詩在變雅美非全</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4288:4305'>　　美也三家不分正變故有美無箴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4305:4309'>沔水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4309:4335'>讒言其興　韓詩薛君曰讒言每縁間而起也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4335:4358'>　　上云民之訛言如檿弧箕服之類故曰寧莫之懲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4358:4382'>　　此云讒言其興則詐偽之言縁間而起反以恭敬忠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4382:4409'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-13a' );" name="007-13a" class="pb">[007-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4409:4426'>　　諫為誹謗如左儒杜伯之死是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4426:4430'>鶴鳴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4430:4452'>鶴鳴于九臯　韓詩九臯九折之澤也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4452:4475'>　　九折之澤至為繚曲而聲聞於天以喻密室陳詞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4475:4498'>　　而天下咸聞其忠讜猶鼔鐘於宫聲聞於外之意</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4498:4521'>　　鄭箋以九臯為坎自外數至内為九似緯家之說</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4521:4525'>白駒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4525:4549'>在彼空谷　韓詩空作穹薛君曰深谷也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4549:4576'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-13b' );" name="007-13b" class="pb">[007-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4576:4580'>斯干</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4580:4603'>　魯詩劉向曰周德既衰而奢侈宣王賢而中興更為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4603:4626'>　儉宫室小寢廟詩人美之斯干之詩是也上章道宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4626:4642'>　室之如制下章言子孫之衆多也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4642:4665'>　　按詩前五章極形宣王宫室之美並無儉小之意</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4665:4688'>　　顧絳謂宣王之世詩多溢美如嵩高蒸民諸篇詞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4688:4711'>　　多夸而不實是詩亦然蓋詩雖有美無刺而入之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4711:4722'>　　變雅當知此意也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4722:4749'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-14a' );" name="007-14a" class="pb">[007-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4749:4774'>如矢斯棘<span class='krp-note'>韓作朸/旅即反</span>如鳥斯革<span class='krp-note'>韓作/□</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4774:4790'>　韓傳朸隅也□翅也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4790:4819'>乃生男子　室家君王　載衣之裼<span class='krp-note'>韓作/<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2103' title='KR2103' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2103.png'/></span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4819:4842'>　韓傳生男以為世子所以為世子者何言世世不絶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4842:4869'>　也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span>太子生以桑弧蓬矢六射上下四方言當有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4869:4908'>　事天地四方也<span class='krp-note'>白虎通/引内傳</span>　齊人名小兒被為<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2103' title='KR2103' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2103.png'/><span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4908:4938'>　　古人名被皆曰衣論語必有寝衣是也<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2103' title='KR2103' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2103.png'/>者褓也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4938:4942'>無羊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4942:4969'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '007-14b' );" name="007-14b" class="pb">[007-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='4969:4988'>或寢或訛　韓傳訛作譌覺也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='4988:4991'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='4991:4994'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='4994:4997'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='4997:5000'>　</span><br/>
